          when it's 120 degrees outside for 8 months of the year... I randomly decided on Denver and could not have picked a better city. I love the
          culture, I love the scenery, and I met my future hubby just 6 weeks after moving here. I've listed some of my favorite hobbies below,
          which I think gives a great summary as to why I love Denver and why I might love programming.
